  "remarks": "Shijiazhuang Hanqiang Technology is a People’s Republic of China-based manufacturer for rock wool machinery. Shijiazhuang Hanqiang Technology exported products of European origin to Russian companies while these products were subject to Union export restrictions, notably to the Centre for Effective Production Solutions (ROSCEPR).",
